    "chunk_id": "docling_jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_3718_6",
    "text": "Tests have shown that children have about ten seconds of \"working memory\" - if a child can read a sentence in ten or less seconds, he/she can \"get\" (comprehend) the \"big idea\" of the sentence.",
